in a previous version of this report dated 20 Mar 2007, published in
Ciencias e Saude:
<http://cienciaesaude.uol.com.br/ultnot/estado/2007/03/20/ult4513u5.jhtm>.
This included information about 3 confirmed, non-fatal cases of DHF
and 8 more suspected DHF cases awaiting confirmation.
